originalText.text: Daimian was a dream to work with! He was always early to our meetings, extremely prompt in our communications, and incredibly helpful throughout the whole process. We always felt like he had our best interests in mind and was trying to get us the best result in what is otherwise a fairly stressful process. We hope to work with Daimian again in the future!

originalText.text: We can't speak highly enough of our experience with Damian. We were first-time homebuyers with very little knowledge about how to find the right place. We met with a couple of realtors before him, but we knew instantly that he was the one for us. He is honest and hands-on, and he really helped to take the pressure off of us. We have several friends looking for homes and thinking about selling, and we always recommend Damian to them!
